{"root":{"data":{"id":"dhaujhp9c0w0","created":1774338603746,"text":"系统架构师"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhaujsax6rc0","created":1774338626823,"text":"软件工程"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhaukbywr1k0","created":1774338669633,"text":"开放模型"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhaukw45fi00","created":1774338713485,"text":"瀑布模型"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhaum6g2hvk0","created":1774338814338,"text":"被称为软件周期型，一个阶段到另一个阶段下降像瀑布"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhaun0v5sds0","created":1774338880554,"text":"前一阶段的成果是后一阶段的输入"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dhaunfoqw0o0","created":1774338912819,"text":"螺旋模型"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhaunnw5vcw0","created":1774338930680,"text":"分支主题"},"children":[]}]}]}]}]},"template":"default","theme":"fresh-blue","version":"1.4.43"}